title: Venom: Funeral Pyre
body:
Coming as a complete surprise to me, Venom’s the talk of the town! After the recent film, which I didn’t think was super great, and a few new series Marvel is putting out, one of which put the symbiote back on Brock, people actually know who he is again. Who would’ve guessed anyone would still care about a giant buff goo-man with sharp fangs and a slobbery tongue? Well, anyone aside from me. I always cared. Even when he was stupid. Especially when he’s stupid. Like this.

summary:
The other
night, I had a dream where I was in a relationship (crazy, right?), and my
boyfriend proposed to me using a golden...
body: The other night, I had a dream where I was in a relationship (crazy, right?), and my boyfriend proposed to me using a golden ring with six different kind of precious stones: emeralds, diamonds, a rose diamond I think, etc. When he was putting the ring on my finger, I realized they were the same colors as the Infinity Stones. I asked him about it, and he said “for all the power you hold over me, for all that you have my world in your hands, you might as well be a generous, beautiful version of Thanos. OR, you know, Captain Marvel as well”. And, the sad thing, is that no one else will ever out do dream-boyfriend. He raised my expectations in man incredibly high.

summary: i posted this on my twitter already but let me share my small theory here we know the events of far from home take place after...
body:
i posted this on my twitter already but let me share my small theory here

we know the events of far from home take place after a4, with peter being alive and well thank god, but also he gets a new suit like he did in infinity war

so i’ve been looking at it again:

in infinity war, we see that the suit tony’s made for peter is colorful and shiny, just how he likes his iron man suits, however in far from home, they introduce a new suit that looks extremely pulled back, more streamlined:

look a little familiar?

you can see the aesthetic/texture of the black fabric is very similar to t’challa’s black panther suit and how different the red and black suit is to the flashiness of the iron spider suit, so it’s clear that it couldn’t have been made by tony, and we know peter couldn’t design a suit by himself, tony would also NEVER let anyone else design a suit for peter other than him

so what i believe is that tony will die in a4 and shuri will step in to help peter in far from home
